        <num>CC 2050</num>
        <heading>2050.  Provisions interpreted in light of each other</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2050.  Provisions interpreted in light of each other
Each provision in a contract must be interpreted in light of the other provisions so that each is given the meaning suggested by the contract as a whole.</p>
        </content>
